name: Fish&Richardson
0:
”Alexa, ask Fish and Richardson for the latest news”
”Text that to me”
”Alexa, ask Fish and Richardson for the app”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fish and richardson
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Stay up to date on the latest news from Fish & Richardson. With this skill you can...

* Hear the latest Fish and Richardson Facebook posts
* Have any post texted to your phone
* Get the links to the official Fish and Richardson mobile app

A great way to keep informed using just your voice.
